[SN]TITLE[SN]
Oscar Pistorius sentenced to six years for murder of Reeva Steenkamp

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Judge Thokozile Masipa sentences South African Paralympic athlete Oscar Pistorius to six years in prison for the murder of his girlfriend Reeva Steenkamp in 2013.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
6 July 2016 Last updated at 10:35 BST
It comes after his initial five-year conviction for manslaughter was changed to murder last December on appeal.
